headline: TempraMed Announces Strategic Agreement with Maccabi Healthcare Services, a Leading HMO with over 2.8 Million Patients

headline: 1 Healthcare Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 We Brush Off
summary: Personal health and wellness is one of the many secular tailwinds for healthcare companies. Players catalyzing medical advancements have benefited from elevated demand, which has supported the industry’s returns lately - over the past six months, healthcare stocks have gained 13.5%, nearly mirrorring the S&P 500.
